# Optional: override the socket.io websocket target.
# - Leave blank in dev (Vite proxies /socket.io to localhost:4000 for you).
# - Set in production (Cloudflare Pages) to the API origin so realtime alerts
#   reach the right host. Without this, socket.io tries the SPA's own origin
#   (Cloudflare Pages), which doesn't host a websocket server, and realtime
#   silently falls back to the 15s polling.
#
# Example for our Fly.io deploy:
# VITE_WS_URL=https://lightning-risk-api.fly.dev
VITE_WS_URL=
